data.description: Ranch style on full basement with open floor plan.  3 BR 2 Full baths upstairs with ceramic sinktops. All custom cabinets throughout house.  Granite countertops, stainless steel Samsung Appliances.  Large bedrooms, Master BR has 2 large walk in closets with dressing area leading into Master bath.  Skylight in kitchen, oversized windows in guest BRs.  Downstairs has large den with custom cabinets covering one end. Fireplace in center of room.  Also has full bath and laundry room.  Unfinished basement is approx 996 sq ft.  Heat pump and furnace replaced in 2018, water heater replaced in 2019.   Front porch is brick pavers.  Good size deck on back of house, patio at walk out basement.  Oversize carport.  Lot size is .61 acres.
data.whatILove: Wonderful, quiet neighborhood.  Close proximity to Drewry Mason Elementary School and Magna Vista High School.
